<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
{% load static %}
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>User Management System</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-red: #e63946;
            --light-red: #ff6b6b;
            --dark-red: #d00000;
            --white: #f1faee;
            --off-white: #f8f9fa;
            --glass-color: rgba(240, 240, 245, 0.15);
            --glass-border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            --glass-blur: blur(15px);
            --text-color: #333;
            --border-radius: 16px;
            --accent-color: rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.85);
            --dark-overlay: rgba(60, 60, 70, 0.3);
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            background-image: url("{% static 'lmc.jpg' %}");
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: var(--text-color);
            position: relative;
        }
        
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            backdrop-filter: blur(1px);
            background-color: var(--dark-overlay);
            z-index: -1;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: var(--primary-red);
            backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
            border: var(--glass-border);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem 0;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .header p {
            margin: 10px 0 0;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .navbar {
            background: rgba(230, 230, 240, 0.4);
            backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            border-bottom: var(--glass-border);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .navbar a {
            color: var(--primary-red);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: rgba(240, 240, 245, 0.6);
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.3);
        }
        
        .navbar a:hover {
            background: var(--primary-red);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
            flex: 1;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .content-section {
            background: rgba(235, 235, 240, 0.5);
            backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
            border: var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            color: var(--text-color);
        }
        
        .content-section h2 {
            color: var(--primary-red);
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.2);
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .content-section p {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111111;
            text-shadow: 0 1px 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }
        
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        
        .feature-card {
            background: rgba(230, 230, 240, 0.5);
            backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
            border: 1px solid rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.2);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .feature-card::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-red), var(--light-red));
            transform: translateY(-100%);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.2);
            border-color: var(--primary-red);
        }
        
        .feature-card:hover::after {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        
        .feature-card h3 {
            color: var(--primary-red);
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .feature-card p {
            color: #111111;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-shadow: 0 1px 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--primary-red);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 0.9rem 1.8rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            margin-top: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.3);
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            background: var(--dark-red);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: var(--primary-red);
            backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
            border-top: var(--glass-border);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        li {
            margin: 0 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>User Management System</h1>
        <p>A simple Django application to manage user profiles</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="navbar">
        <ul>
            <li><a href="{% url 'home' %}">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="{% url 'index' %}">Register</a></li>
            <li><a href="{% url 'show_form' %}">User List</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content-section">
            <h2>Welcome to the User Management System</h2>
            <p>This application allows you to perform basic CRUD operations on user profiles:</p>
            
            <div class="features">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Create Users</h3>
                    <p>Add new users to the system with username, email, and password.</p>
                    <a href="{% url 'index' %}" class="btn">Register Now</a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>View Users</h3>
                    <p>See all users in a clean, organized table format.</p>
                    <a href="{% url 'show_form' %}" class="btn">View Users</a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Update Users</h3>
                    <p>Modify existing user information as needed.</p>
                    <a href="{% url 'show_form' %}" class="btn">Manage Users</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>made with &hearts;</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
